Text: does it have the android part?

instructions, when done installing:

1. Copy Crack and License into folder

2. run crack file [main program thing] and there will be the option to continue or something...

3. After you continue it will talk about internet and manual activation.. do manual.. then one button will say something like [read license].. click that and then browse to the license file.

DONE.. took me a bit to figure out due to the weird wording. The right button makes it sound like you'll be reading their terms and conditions.. but no it will read the cracked license.
